      "created_at": "2024-01-10T08:35:55.407Z",
      "cooked": "<aside class=\"quote group-English\" data-username=\"Alex\" data-post=\"5\" data-topic=\"31229\">\n<div class=\"title\">\n<div class=\"quote-controls\"></div>\n<img loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" src=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/user_avatar/forums.trainerday.com/alex/48/1331_2.png\" class=\"avatar\"> Alex:</div>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Chasing maximum fitness score can be fun and motivate you.</p>\n</blockquote>\n</aside>\n<p>Indeed it does <img src=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/images/emoji/twitter/wink.png?v=12\" title=\":wink:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":wink:\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\"><br>\nBut for the next time period I\u2019ll be patient and will not focus on the fitness curve</p>",
