      "created_at": "2024-01-10T08:44:39.011Z",
      "cooked": "<p>Yes, it\u2019s safer to wait, if you are in good shape and have a good base and want to chase some short term fitness gains it can be very good and motivating.  This is especially valuable towards the end of a build and peak period of training.</p>",
      "post_number": 9,
